- What?

228
00:22:10,248 --> 00:22:15,122
Should I tell uncle and aunty?

229
00:22:15,123 --> 00:22:16,372
No...Anu!

230
00:22:16,373 --> 00:22:18,247
Anu! Please stop, please.

231
00:22:18,248 --> 00:22:19,997
Stop all this nonsense.

232
00:22:19,998 --> 00:22:23,206
