- No, no, no!

546
00:46:51,123 --> 00:46:52,456
I'm going. I'm going home.

547
00:46:52,457 --> 00:46:54,331
I'm not going for the show.
I'm going home.

548
00:46:54,332 --> 00:46:57,247
