I can actually see someone.

647
00:54:45,123 --> 00:54:48,372
I can see a girl.
That kind of "seeing".

648
00:54:48,373 --> 00:54:50,497
I can see a ghost.
I...l can see a ghost.

649
00:54:50,498 --> 00:54:54,872
Shut up!

650
00:54:54,873 --> 00:54:57,706
Enough...

651
00:54:57,707 --> 00:55:00,706
