"And you brought me to my senses."

1125
01:50:04,290 --> 01:50:06,414
"You are my truth."

1126
01:50:06,415 --> 01:50:08,456
"And I bow down to you."

1127
01:50:08,457 --> 01:50:10,831
"You are my truth."

1128
