1131
01:50:22,290 --> 01:50:25,622
"Don't abandon me, dear heart."

1132
01:50:25,623 --> 01:50:30,623
"I am nothing without you."

1133
01:50:30,707 --> 01:50:33,706
"Dear heart..."

1134
01:50:33,707 --> 01:50:37,081
"This pain of separation
wounds me.“

1135
01:50:37,082 --> 01:50:39,747
"Dear heart..."

1136
